title: Delve (NSFW Web Comic) - Complete through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"DELVE" Web Comic

"Delve" (delvecomic.com) by Andrew Hunter is a humorous fantasy comic following the adventures of Bree Starval, a wood elf rogue.  She entered "The Delve," home of the mysterious dracomage, in the company of a party of adventurers.  But after her group was attacked by lizard men in an unfamiliar and dangerous section of the dungeon, her companions fled, leaving Bree at the mercy of Ssithikus, King of the Lizardians, who mates with all female trespassers.  And thus the tone for the series was set.  The comic features no sex, but there is a great deal of nudity, so it's definitely NSFW.

This torrent collects the "Delve" comic from its beginning in 2009 through the close of chapter 8 at the end of 2014
